Package cards.career_cards

Provides the classes for the career cards, which dictates the player's career, degree requirement (whether it is required or not), and maximum number of pay raises
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Accountant
    Class implementing an Accountant career card, which dictates the player's career, degree requirement (whether it is required or not), and maximum number of pay raises associated with being an accountant

    RacecarDriver
    Class implementing a Racecar Driver career card, which dictates the player's career, degree requirement (whether it is required or not), and maximum number of pay raises associated with being a racecar driver
    Server
    Class implementing a Server career card, which dictates the player's career, degree requirement (whether it is required or not), and maximum number of pay raises associated with being a server
